                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7 pt-4">
                    <h3>Seamless and Secure Marathon Event Registration</h3>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Join our marathon events effortlessly with our user-friendly registration system. Get ready to be part of an unforgettable running experience.
